'''Uddis agman''' d yal [[uddis akruran|uddis]] dgi [[acubar|icubar-is]] lan (sɛan) [[akaṛbun]] (s unagar n [[Kaṛbid|Ukaṛbid]], [[Kaṛbunat]], [[Asnuksid n ukaṛbun]], [[Bikaṛbunat]], [[Syanat]]).
Tiɣri n uddis agman tettusemma [[Takrura tagmant]], Yerna aṭas n uddisen-a am: [[Pṛutin|Tepṛutinin]], [[Lipid|ilipiden]] akk d [[Kaṛbuhidr|ikaṛbuhidren]] lant (sɛant) azal muqqren deg tussna n  [[takrudert|tekrudert]]

Irem n '''agman''' d awal amezray yettuɣalen ar [[Awines wis 17|uwines wis 17]] 

Azal ameqran n uddisen igmanen zeddigen twasxdamen-d s tamugri|tmugri]] ɣas akken isem-is ''Agman'' (ẓeṛ [[taseddat tagmant]])



